@startuml
[*] --> LoggedIn
LoggedIn --> ViewingJourneyDetails : View Journey Details
ViewingJourneyDetails --> DrivingModeActivated : Activate Driving Mode
DrivingModeActivated --> AccidentOccurred : Accident Occurs
AccidentOccurred --> NotificationsSent : Inform Authorities
NotificationsSent --> FeedbackProvided : Send Notifications
FeedbackProvided --> [*] : Provide Feedback

ViewingJourneyDetails --> OtherOptionsSelected : Choose Other Options
OtherOptionsSelected --> EatingSelected : Select Place to Eat
EatingSelected --> MenuViewing : View Menu
MenuViewing --> OrderPlaced : Place Order
OrderPlaced --> ViewingJourneyDetails : Continue Journey

DrivingModeActivated --> JourneyDetails : Deactivate
JourneyDetails --> ViewingJourneyDetails : View Details Again

OtherOptionsSelected --> ViewingJourneyDetails : View Details Again

EatingSelected --> ViewingJourneyDetails : Finish Eating

AccidentOccurred --> ViewingJourneyDetails : View Details Again

ViewingJourneyDetails --> FeedbackProvided : Complete Journey

@enduml
